name: Potato Combo
description: As the name says, this is the Potato Festival at CriptoBurguer! We have a delicious Crispy Breaded Potato with tomato, mushrooms, onions, lettuce, mustard and pickles, a glass of Grape juice, Smile fries, and a Brazilian candy made of sweet potato! Everything is so yummy that Mr. Potato Head himself came to our Burger shop. Note: HLE= "Happiness level after eat it"
